{"tid":1507712,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【反修例】東區醫院醫護逾700人實名聯署 轟警方阻人道救援","createTime":"2019-08-26T09:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T14:56:14.000Z","uid":212626,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ed3b54ca7a8a1cff43b363fe44d71a95323a5629","tid":1507712,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:17:01.000Z","msg":"反修例爭議持續，東區醫院逾700個醫護人員今（26日）公開一份<span style=\"color: red;\">實名聯署</span>，盼特首林鄭月娥正視回應5大訴求；又批評警方於處理社會運動的手法是草菅人命，並指摘警方多次阻礙人道救援工作，深表遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n聯署聲明指出，警察以拘捕示威者為由，於集會範圍阻礙救護車進出，剝奪示威者人權；聲明又稱警方多次攻擊已表明身分、並拘捕在場醫療人員，認為這令救援受阻，也違反國際人權法。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又稱，對於有警員近日試圖於醫院急症室，搜捕懷疑示威者；聯署醫護重申，醫院不容暴力事件發生，是救治傷患的地方，嚴正抗議警方肆意進入，令病人、醫護感人身安全受威脅，他們呼籲警方不應以執法為理由，阻礙人道救援。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又指，醫護人員天職是救治傷患，不受政見左右。他們恪守以人命為重，又以病人為先，也秉持醫護專業立場，盡心救治病人。作為醫護，他們承諾保持應有操守，為病人服務，跟香港人並肩同行。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2436035/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2436035%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYy3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=a32786b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2436035/</a>"},{"pid":"afb466398aadbf3cc733504f4dfffd55ff464865","tid":1507712,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:17:12.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYy3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=abe06100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"82441360706ce998e8df227c43c14c9651b397c9","tid":1507712,"uid":286639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:17:49.000Z","msg":"[緊急]快啲快手入嚟send email<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n借推"},{"pid":"1a15ab17bab5464063a733ae1efeae5b64ea196b","tid":1507712,"uid":14148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:19:29.000Z","msg":"多謝醫生護士👨🏻&zwj;⚕️👩🏻&zwj;⚕️"},{"pid":"38cb24b456df53e253147e83b77b55f1b0e116dd","tid":1507712,"uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:19:38.000Z","msg":"東區醫院超過700名醫護聯署，包括有醫生、護士、化驗師放射師、物理治療師、文員等。他們斥政府放縱警方濫權及使用暴力，令示威者以至普羅市民身受嚴重傷害，更多次妨害傷者求治。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，警方迄今使用接近2000發催淚彈，有市民受催淚煙影響相繼出現呼吸系統、腸道及皮膚病狀，老人及小孩尤為嚴重。有指警方於行動中曾經使用過期催淚彈，警方至今未有否認。專家指出過期催淚彈發射後經加熱有機會釋出山埃、光氣等有毒氣體，難以估計其對市民健康影響。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZ0nLPu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZ0nLPu.png&h=efa5f5f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%80%BE-700-%E5%90%8D%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E5%AF%A6%E5%90%8D%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E6%96%A5%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%A6%A8%E7%A4%99%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4-%E5%89%9D%E5%A5%AA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A/?fbclid=IwAR1BsifMA_SxIXNmQpbgc9zIWIcYuvJFOExN_JAdgKXqWxb3zvDQ394mD4o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2580%25BE-700-%25E5%2590%258D%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E6%2596%25A5%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25A6%25A8%25E7%25A4%2599%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%2595%2591%25E6%258F%25B4-%25E5%2589%259D%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1BsifMA_SxIXNmQpbgc9zIWIcYuvJFOExN_JAdgKXqWxb3zvDQ394mD4o&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYy3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=48fd21c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2586%25AB%2